Asteroid13Level.description:
POPULATION: Deceased/Mutated
CONDITIONS: Cold, hard rocky terrain, no surface plant life detected.
FAUNA: A dead ecosystem.

DesolationLevel.description:
POPULATION: Left/Deceased.
CONDITIONS: Dead, desolate landscape, no healthy flora present.
FAUNA: A dying ecosystem, remaining fauna display agressive behaviour.

FissionCLevel.description:
POPULATION: Gone.
CONDITIONS: Hot dry toxic terrain, no surviving flora.
FAUNA: An irradiated ecosystem.

AtlanticaLevel.description:
POPULATION: Drowned.
CONDITIONS: Cold wet terrain, supports aquatic plant life.
FAUNA: A healthy ecosystem, fauna supports neutral behaviour.

InfernisLevel.description:
POPULATION: Deceased.
CONDITIONS: Extremely hot, Dry dusty terrain, Rarely supports living plant life due to recent volcanic activity.
FAUNA: A desperate ecosystem, remaining creatures support agressive behaviour.

GloomLevel.description:
POPULATION: Missing.
CONDITIONS: Cold moist terrain, roofed trees present.
FAUNA: A flowering ecosystem, agressive behaviour present.

OldredLevel.description:
POPULATION: Deceased.
CONDITIONS: Hot thin terrain, no surviving flora, high pressure within outer crust.
FAUNA: A desperate ecosystem, remaining fauna display agressive behaviour.

PolarusLevel.description:

CONDITIONS: Cold, wet snowy terrain, supports plant life.
FAUNA: A balanced ecosystem, creatures support very agressive behaviour.

JunicLevel.description:

CONDITIONS: Warm, very lush terrain, supports plenty of flora, always sunny.
FAUNA: A very healthy ecosystem, fauna exhibits neutral behaviour.

CONDITIONS: Warm, dry dirt terrain, supports plant life such as Fabaceae.
FAUNA: A thriving Avian ecosystem, creatures support agressive behaviour.

CONDITIONS: Warm lush terrain, supports pleny of flora, acidic pools present.
FAUNA: A healthy ecosystem, fauna supports neutral behaviour.

CONDITIONS: A landscape of deep valleys and mountains.
FAUNA: Home to a lively, diverse ecosystem of smaller-sized omnivores.

CONDITIONS: Waning forests. Abandoned facilities littered across the landscape.
FAUNA: Rumored active machinery left behind.
